 is pretty clean!)</p>\n<h2>How to Stay Clean</h2>\n<p>There are several preventive maintenance tips that you can use to keep your website hacker free. Nothing is 100% but I am going to follow this post up with some of helpful advice. For now, head to Sucuri.net and ','Help, we just got hacked!','','inherit','open','open','','1-autosave','','','2013-05-02 23:44:09','2013-05-02 23:44:09','',1,'http://localhost:8888/jeremybasham_finalproject_wp/wordpress/?p=21',0,'revision','',0),
